overview: Welcome to Vol. 20(!!) of “Lost & Found Video Night”! Prepare to enter our most self indulgent excursion yet! A NEARLY 2 HOUR extravaganza of everything the “Lost & Found” crew has come to love and wallow in over the years! Andy Kaufman! Weirdo commercials! Public Access whackos! Jack Kerouac! Walerian Borowczyk! Don Cherry! Alex Jones screaming! Negativland on the news! Out of context film clips! Brian Eno! Shecky Greene! Judge Tony Clifton! & a whole lot more!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 20
